      <item>
        <title>Build error on vercel</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[abhishek.kumar]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Yes, it’s resolved now, you need to create a file in root of you project with name <strong>.npmrc</strong> and add this line of code  <code>node-options="--openssl-legacy-provider"</code> in file and then deploy it on vercel. It should work fine.</p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/build-error-on-vercel/6790/5">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
